author: Chelseahavoc
title: Only for a party...
review: While this set looks cute it is completely unplayable. Once the post cards are sent, the straws tagged, and the names reserved; all that is left is to build the flags/name tag holders and paper confetti. And who is going to keep their little flag perfectly built and their name card unbent? This is defiantly a cute idea, however it was poorly executed.
